---
title: Flame-Grilled Chicken & Charred Broccoli with Garlic Herb Potatoes
description: Let’s turn up the heat with this BBQ delight! Smokey grilled chicken pairs perfectly with a vibrant charred broccoli salad,
bringing bold flavours to the table. Toss in some golden garlic herb potatoes and you’ve got a smokey, savoury masterpiece made for al fresco dining. If you don’t have a BBQ, follow our stovetop method!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
